subject: Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race (Alaska)
Dog Sledding
lead_paragraph: Scott Janssen, an Anchorage undertaker known as the Mushing Mortician, was flown to a hospital after a harrowing ordeal in the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race.
